subject: Beautiful work, are any pieces available?
body:
Hi there,
I came across your artwork recently and was really impressed. I'd love to learn more about what you're working on and if anything is currently available.

Best regards,
Jonathan Peterson Miller

subject: Quick question about your artwork
body:
Hello,
Your art caught my eye while I was browsing recently. I'm always on the lookout for original pieces and would love to connect.

Best regards,
Jonathan Peterson Miller

subject: Saw your work and had to reach out
body:
Hi,
I saw one of your pieces online and was genuinely drawn to it. Would you be open to sharing a few available works or your portfolio?

Best regards,
Jonathan Peterson Miller
